  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 10 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0b9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "All 10 independent political parties resolve to support Dalas - Vimal Weerawansa",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "All the members of the 10 independent political parties in the Parliament have decided to support the presidential candidate Dalas Alagaperuma. National Freedom Front leader Vimal Weerawansa insisted that the People's Liberation Front should be united in the all-party government.",
        "He said the above while attending a press conference in Colombo today (19).",
        "Thanks must be given to Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasha. The Leader of the Opposition has taken the best decision considering the current critical situation without prioritizing his personal position regarding the presidency.",
        "It is to be welcomed that Sri Lanka Podujana Peramana Vice President Professor GL Peiris has confirmed that Opposition leader Sajith Premadasa proposed the name of Dulles Alagaperuma.",
        "Prof. GL Peiris' decision has made the ruling parties who had decided to extend support to Ranil Wickremesinghe think twice.",
        "If Dulles Aagaperuma is elected as the president, the government led by opposition leader Sajith Premadasa will be formed by uniting all political parties. People's Liberation Front leader should join the all-party government.",
        "All parties should work together to find a solution to the current economic and social crisis. 225 Parliamentarians should respect the aspirations of the people and take the best decision.",
        "All the members of the 10 independent political parties in Parliament have decided to support the presidential candidate Dalas Alagaperuma. He said that no problem can be solved without establishing a government in which the people of the country trust."
      ],
